Unicode input engine (using Gucharmap) for IBus.

* Install

ibus-gucharmap won't compile with ibus-1.3.  You will need:
ibus-1.0 >= 1.3.99, gucharmap-2.90, and vala.

 $ sudo yum install ibus-devel gucharmap-devel vala
 $ ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr # --libdir=/usr/lib64
 $ make
 $ sudo make install

* Usage

Add ibus-gucharmap with ibus-setup, enable it on a GTK application,
and double-click a Unicode character to input.

